-- Salazar Signs Accord With Cape Wind Associates for Offshore Development
-- B y   B i l l   K o e n i g
-- 2010-10-06T13:13:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-06/salazar-signs-accord-with-cape-wind-associates-for-offshore-development.html
U.S. Interior Secretary Ken Salazar
and Cape Wind Associates LLC today signed the first U.S. lease
for commercial wind energy development on the Outer Continental
Shelf. The information was in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
